              income  year (%)  assets  year (%)    1993-94   1992-93
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------
Nippon Life    5,790      +3.7  34,719      +8.3       3.48      4.16
Mutual Life    4,034      +0.3  24,295      +7.5       3.36      3.90
Life           3,615      +1.3  21,398      +8.0       3.91      4.14
Mutual Life    2,586      -0.7  14,825      +9.1       4.16      4.31
