FT  10 JUN 94 / World Trade News: OECD Export Credit Rates
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
 ---------------------------------------------------------------------- THE
Organisation for Economic Co-operation and Development announced new minimum
interest rates (%) for officially-supported export credits for June 15 to
July 14 1994 (May 15 1994 - June 14 1994 in brackets).
 ----------------------------------------------------------------------
